claim.claim-text:
1. A communications device comprising:
at least one function-identifier table for storing one or more of a non-numeric code prefix or a service code programmed for identifying a service invocation;
an interface in the communication device configured to receive an input sequence that includes an input function code that identifies a service invocation;
a processing engine in the communication device, the processing engine being communicatively coupled to the interface and being operative to determine if the input function code identifies a service invocation corresponding to a function identifier stored in the function-identifier table;
wherein:
the processing engine is operable, in response to determining that the input function code identifies the service invocation, to transmit information related to the service invocation; and
the communication device is operable to establish a connection with a service-fulfillment center and to receive therefrom, during a communication between the communication device and the service-fulfillment center, dynamic reprogramming operative to alter contents of the function-identifier table.

8. A method for permitting a user to invoke a service with a communication device in a communication network, comprising:
programming the communication device with at least one function-identifier table containing one or more of a non-numeric code prefix or a service code for triggering service invocation;
receiving an input sequence at the communication device to identify a service invocation;
determining that a function identifier in the input sequence that includes a non-numeric code prefix identifies a service invocation corresponding to a function identifier stored in the function-identifier table;
in response to determining that the function identifier identifies the service invocation, transmitting information related to the service invocation to a service-fulfillment center,
wherein, during a communication between the communication device and the service-fulfillment center, the communication device receives dynamic reprogramming operative to alter contents of the function-identifier table.
